Company Overview of Blackstone Tactical Opportunities Fund L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Blackstone Tactical Opportunities Fund L.P. specializes in buyouts, financial institution breakups, re-insurance, and improving freight mobility. The fund seeks to invest in shipping, real estate, corporate or consumer loans, and alternative energy. The fund prefers to take majority stake in its portfolio companies. It has a three year investment period.


